    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes modifications of BGP Labeled Unicast (BGP-LU) procedures for label distribution in a partitioned network. Specifically, these procedures are suitable for building the Hierarchical SDN (HSDN) control plane for the hyper-scale Data Center (DC) and cloud networks.</t>
